        },
        "subject": "LU-17885 osc: convert cdp_page_count to int",
        "message": "LU-17885 osc: convert cdp_page_count to int\n\nAs wild as it sounds, 2% of CPU time in DIO is spent in\nhandling a 32 bit sign extension for this value when used\nin the loop check in osc_transfer_page_init.\n\nThere is no need for more than 32 bits of pages.\n\nTest-Parameters: forjanitoronly\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <paf0187@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: I13842b3e7129e7faeea43c67d3f641c0bd6e3003\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
